gmxp_res = self.do_command(self.get_password_args() + ['-f', self.
    fingerprint, 'getmasterxpub'])
self.assertEqual(gmxp_res['xpub'], self.master_xpub)
gmxp_res = self.do_command(self.get_password_args() + ['-f', '0000ffff',
    'getmasterxpub'])
self.assertEqual(gmxp_res['error'],
    'Could not find device with specified fingerprint')
self.assertEqual(gmxp_res['code'], -3)
